{"tid":2086182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跪有咩問題？識唔識咩叫留有用之身？一直講緊哩個係長期戰。","createTime":"2020-06-30T07:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T14:25:50.000Z","uid":113155,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb19724a8e3c699d07935263807ab44def29655","tid":2086182,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">低成本抗爭諗住速贏？<br />\n會唔會太樂觀。<br />\n我哋一直係雞蛋，跪有咩問題？<br />\n退黃圈就唔黃？油顏色咩⋯⋯<br />\n不嬲冇大台，眾志散咗咪散咗，國際線仲喺度，着緊添。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成班放負做乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n藍絲請聽住：以前大家笑柒北韓領導死咗國民哭喪有幾搞笑，過兩日輪到全世界笑柒你跪哋講「雜總萬歲萬歲萬萬歲啦。」<br />\n<br />\n五毛請聽住：有個迷語，有個國家，高官和商人每天都讚美自己國家，數落別國，但全把子女送外國讀書，資產放外國，有錢了便全家移民或拿外國國際。請猜一國家。"},{"pid":"8376c7648d323e7e9bd9b46dbd8a9e64d62cc18e","tid":2086182,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4a01ee9467c68ac7fb8e2571717adccf5002d4","tid":2086182,"uid":113155,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"但勇武我建議聽日唔好出，繼續休養養身。<br />\n國家係保障鳩拉無罪，所以請好好珍惜自己。"},{"pid":"b9406ed848865437bf14650f404efbf047a656dd","tid":2086182,"uid":217874,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒唔係得個講字 大家要有心理準備<br />\n香港人係對抗緊一個極權國家 全球第二大經濟體<br />\n唔好諗住一年半載就可以贏到<br />\n放負撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9b33c99ccf4cde63b1f612a280255cd0b6161c","tid":2086182,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f